(405, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2017/09/wordpress-4-8-2-security-and-maintenance-release/''>WordPress 4.8.2 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">September 19, 2017</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.8.2 is now available. This is a security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. WordPress versions 4.8.1 and earlier are affected by these security issues: $wpdb-&gt;prepare() can create unexpected and unsafe queries leading to potential SQL injection (SQLi). WordPress core is not directly vulnerable to this [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/donatewc-reaches-fundraising-goal''>WPTavern: DonateWC Reaches Fundraising Goal</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/wordcamp-for-publishers-videos-now-available-on-youtube''>WPTavern: WordCamp for Publishers Videos Now Available on YouTube</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/apply-filters-podcast-to-be-retired-after-83-episodes''>WPTavern: Apply Filters Podcast to be Retired after 83 Episodes</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><br />\n<font size=''1''><table class=''xdebug-error xe-notice'' dir=''ltr'' border=''1'' cellspacing=''0'' cellpadding=''1''>\n<tr><th align=''left'' bgcolor=''#f57900'' colspan="5"><span style=''background-color: #cc0000; color: #fce94f; font-size: x-large;''>( ! )</span> Notice: Undefined offset: 1 in /vagrant/html/wordpress/wp-admin/includes/dashboard.php on line <i>1115</i></th></tr>\n<tr><th align=''left'' bgcolor=''#e9b96e'' colspan=''5''>Call Stack</th></tr>\n<tr><th align=''center'' bgcolor=''#eeeeec''>#</th><th align=''left'' bgcolor=''#eeeeec''>Time</th><th align=''left'' bgcolor=''#eeeeec''>Memory</th><th align=''left'' bgcolor=''#eeeeec''>Function</th><